data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of a quiet neighborhood! This delightful abode is perfect for those seeking a balance between tranquility and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an  inviting living space that exudes warmth and character. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends and family. The three bedrooms offer a peaceful retreat, each boasting its own unique charm and ample natural light. The two bathrooms are designed to offer a touch of luxury and convenience. Outside, you'll discover a backyard oasis that is perfect for relaxation and play.  Let’s not forget about the neighborhood! This community is known for its excellent schools, ensuring that your little ones will receive a top-notch education. Plus, the quiet streets and friendly neighbors create a welcoming atmosphere that you'll love coming home to. This home would be perfect as your first home or an investment property. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming home yours with a NEW 2020 ROOF and TWO AC units for under $250k! It's the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, just waiting for you to add your personal touch.
